data.name: Miracle Jurassic Egg
data.desc: While face-up on the field, this card cannot be banished. Each time a Dinosaur-Type monster(s) is sent to your Graveyard, place 2 counters on this card. You can Tribute this card; Special Summon 1 Dinosaur-Type monster from your Deck whose Level is less than or equal to the number of counters that were on this card.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 4: Joey's World Mega Pack
